{%- comment -%}
Section: Hero - Lifestyle Final (100% Polish: Depth & Affordance)
Changes:
1. ARROW AFFORDANCE: Changed Dock arrows from generic grey to Kale Green (40% opacity). This improves clickability cues while matching the brand.
2. ICON SCALING: Increased dock icon size from 85% to 92% to fill the container better and improve scannability on mobile.
3. CARD DEPTH: Upgraded the Dock Card shadow to a "Dual Layer" drop shadow. This creates a crisp separation between the menu and the plate image underneath.
{%- endcomment -%}

